onant lines such as Hydrogen H-alpha and HeII1640 will be crucial to\nsearch for clearer signatures of cosmological gas accretion onto galaxies and\nAGN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2016 22:03:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-31"}
