 final\nresult utilizes number-theoretic machinery to estimate the number of solutions\nto a Diophantine equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2016 01:58:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 2 Sep 2017 17:11:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-22"}
