, and robust to the\nsize of the corpus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2016 07:45:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Mar 2017 12:36:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-10"}
