able phase\npropagation velocities mitigates the influence of sky waves and ground effects\nin long-range lightning location networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2016 09:05:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-05"}
