 uniqueness of globally\nattracting positive fixed point in the part of a normal, solid cone. Our\nresults can be applied to well-known stochastic Goodwin negative feedback\nsystem, Othmer-Tyson positive feedback system and Griffith positive feedback\nsystem as well as other stochastic cooperative, competitive and predator-prey\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2016 13:49:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-05"}
